Package: sportyR
Title: Plot ggplot2 Representations of Sports Playing Surfaces
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Ross", "Drucker", email = "ross.a.drucker@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Ross Drucker <ross.a.drucker@gmail.com>
Description: An R package for creating ggplot2 representations of playing
    surfaces. Playing surfaces are drawn pursuant to rule-book specifications.
    This package should be used as a baseline plot for displaying player
    tracking data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    glue,
    rjson,
    utils,
    dplyr
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.3)
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    vdiffr (>= 0.3.3),
    roxygen2
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/rossdrucker/sportyR
BugReports: https://github.com/rossdrucker/sportyR/issues
